@node Main "W-Anim"

                                               @{b}W-Anim 1.1@{ub}



	W-Anim is a small IFF-Anim5 viewer. It is different of Viewtek because it plays the animation into an intuition window. It is not as fast as VT, but you are on your WB screen and this is the more important thing on my opinion.

					@{"    The Author      " link Author}
					@{"    Installation    " link Installation}
					@{"       Usage        " link Usage}
					@{"      Credits       " link Credits}
					@{"       Status       " link Status}


@endnode

